{"tid":837817,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★呂先生：居住於公司名義持有物業，申請新一期居屋 待樓價升值轉售","createTime":"2018-09-26T15:58:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-27T04:01:32.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c58dfbd474247ad15bb3a0711a81cb3136b4b6d8","tid":837817,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T15:58:47.000Z","msg":"最新一期居屋凱樂苑、啟朗苑及裕泰苑，將於10月3日起重啟接受申請，並於今日（26日）開始派表。<br />\n<br />\n從事地產代理的呂先生與家人同住於以公司名義持有的物業，他表示，計劃與家人一家四口共同申請居屋，若成功中籤，將會自己一個人住。呂先生解釋，與家人共同申請是期望附合申請者收入限制，他甚至有考慮聯同祖父母等長者申請，增加成功機會，但指祖父母輩名下已有物業，故未能「借人頭」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1906013/org/69e7fde1a6f3f2c907edd955b5cee1f6.jpg/Dp3qeBkJjunsAu7FwVMKsC2nzSFHX3yG7TycVO08nFQ?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1906013%2Forg%2F69e7fde1a6f3f2c907edd955b5cee1f6.jpg%2FDp3qeBkJjunsAu7FwVMKsC2nzSFHX3yG7TycVO08nFQ%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=2cf4d5b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呂先生看準啟德和長沙灣發展潛力大，期望將來樓價升值時，將居屋補地價轉售。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/239966/%E6%96%B0%E5%B1%85%E5%B1%8B2018-%E6%9C%89%E6%A8%93%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB-%E9%83%BD%E6%94%9E%E8%A1%A8-%E6%8A%BD%E4%B8%AD%E5%95%9F%E5%BE%B7-%E9%95%B7%E6%B2%99%E7%81%A3%E5%B1%85%E5%B1%8B%E6%9C%83%E8%BD%89%E5%94%AE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F239966%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25B1%2585%25E5%25B1%258B2018-%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%25A8%2593%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A3%25AB-%25E9%2583%25BD%25E6%2594%259E%25E8%25A1%25A8-%25E6%258A%25BD%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2595%259F%25E5%25BE%25B7-%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%25B2%2599%25E7%2581%25A3%25E5%25B1%2585%25E5%25B1%258B%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25BD%2589%25E5%2594%25AE&d=PUc9GgcopHu7ojsgqDnXgBxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=c5e50453\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/239966/%E6%96%B0%E5%B1%85%E5%B1%